Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.10,0:00:07.51,Natsu-Italic,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,I've had this image in my \Nhead since I was a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.66,0:00:12.52,Natsu-Italic,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,An image of a landscape \Nyou could find anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.14,0:00:16.46,Natsu-Italic,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,A scene from a dream that \NI have all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.38,0:00:20.93,Natsu-Italic,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,But I've never been there.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.22,0:00:25.79,Natsu-Italic,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,I've been told it's because I've \Nundergone In-Grove's Anti-Feminus.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.79,0:00:28.29,Natsu-Italic,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,But it didn't really matter why.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.14,0:00:32.78,Natsu-Italic,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,I just wanted to search for something.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.63,0:00:36.25,Natsu-Italic,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I went on this trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.94,0:00:41.14,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? An emergency?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.95,0:00:48.19,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,I'm hitting debris? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.42,0:00:51.60,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,There aren't any cleaners this far out...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.54,0:00:53.70,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.70,0:00:54.53,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Rinon!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.53,0:00:55.56,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Take control of the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.42,0:00:58.47,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Make a short jump as soon \Nas the ship is stable!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.97,0:00:59.80,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.20,0:01:02.82,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Take me to that place!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.01,0:01:18.27,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Just... a little farther...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.64,0:01:21.80,Natsu-Italic,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,There's a life-sign in the crash zone?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.53,0:01:25.73,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,I'd likely...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.51,0:01:29.67,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,...been searching for that place.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.78,0:03:02.99,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Nanami-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.13,0:03:04.22,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Nanami-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.66,0:03:08.00,Natsu-Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Kanna-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.37,0:03:11.49,Natsu-Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, man. I had this weird dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.49,0:03:16.84,Natsu-Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,This naked girl was holding Kai-kun\Nwhile they were surrounded by light.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.84,0:03:19.31,Natsu-Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,The girl was really adorable.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.31,0:03:22.85,Natsu-Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,No, she was very beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.85,0:03:26.78,Natsu-Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, she looked exactly like \Nthat girl sitting over...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.84,0:03:28.76,Natsu-Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,...there?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.98,0:03:30.81,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Na—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.81,0:03:32.23,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Nanami-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.07,0:03:38.35,Natsu-Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Could you explain exactly what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.75,0:03:41.50,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Just let me say this:\NDon't get the wrong idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.50,0:03:43.05,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,What idea would that be?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.05,0:03:45.85,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,What you're thinking right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.85,0:03:47.37,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, she's—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.37,0:03:48.71,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Ichika Takatsuki-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.53,0:03:52.48,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,She transferred into the third year \Nclass at our school today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.88,0:03:53.71,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.71,0:03:55.86,Natsu-Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,So your name's Ichika Takatsuki-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.86,0:03:57.15,Natsu-Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.15,0:03:59.51,Natsu-Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Kai-kun's older sister, Nanami.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.51,0:04:01.19,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for having me in your home.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.19,0:04:02.62,Natsu-Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.62,0:04:07.39,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,So? Why is she at your house, Kai-kun,\Nwhen you've only just met today?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.39,0:04:09.09,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,I, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.09,0:04:10.36,Natsu-Main,Icihka,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.69,0:04:13.00,Natsu-Main,Icihka,0000,0000,0000,,Th-There was a malfunction \Nin the quan linkage,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.00,0:04:14.16,Natsu-Main,Icihka,0000,0000,0000,,and my altalite was seriously damaged,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.16,0:04:15.69,Natsu-Main,Icihka,0000,0000,0000,,so I couldn't go anywhere,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.69,0:04:17.14,Natsu-Main,Icihka,0000,0000,0000,,and the damage to the \Nincrobe was extensive...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.14,0:04:20.38,Natsu-Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,That's all too hard for \NOnee-chan to understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.38,0:04:23.28,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Basically, she has nowhere to \Nlive due to some problems,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.28,0:04:25.42,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,and it seems she has no money, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.42,0:04:27.59,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,I just happened to run into her \Non the way home from school,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.59,0:04:28.81,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,and she told me the story.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.81,0:04:31.88,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,So I told her she could \Nstay here for a night...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.20,0:04:34.32,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, you couldn't just walk \Naway after hearing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.32,0:04:37.29,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,You can't have a girl camping \Nout somewhere by herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.82,0:04:39.57,Natsu-Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,So that's what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.57,0:04:40.43,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Question.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.63,0:04:42.93,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Why were you two\Nembracing by the front door?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.19,0:04:45.06,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,We weren't!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.06,0:04:46.19,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,That was...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.19,0:04:47.53,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,We were?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.53,0:04:49.53,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Ka-Kaito-kun's altalite...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.53,0:04:53.74,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,I-I mean, he wasn't feeling well,\Nso I was just taking care of him!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.39,0:04:55.77,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.26,0:05:00.11,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,I started to feel sick and \Nlost consciousness...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.11,0:05:01.45,Natsu-Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Kai-kun, are you sick?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.45,0:05:02.20,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.20,0:05:04.88,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure, but I'm fine now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.82,0:05:06.82,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Taking care of him...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.53,0:05:09.02,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,That's what you were doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.80,0:05:11.92,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Holding him close to you \Nso he gets better...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.58,0:05:15.38,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,That's "taking care of him," all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.77,0:05:18.66,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Did you think he'd get better \Nif you embraced him?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.43,0:05:21.00,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,That's what we do on my planet!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.18,0:05:23.43,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Your planet?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.64,0:05:25.89,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,I-I mean, where I come from.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.89,0:05:28.20,Natsu-Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you from, Takatsuki-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.20,0:05:28.86,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Ple—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.86,0:05:30.59,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,No, I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.95,0:05:32.19,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,North of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.19,0:05:33.84,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Like, Hokkaido?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.84,0:05:35.94,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,No, farther away than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.94,0:05:36.85,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Are you studying abroad?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.23,0:05:39.83,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah, something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.83,0:05:44.11,Natsu-Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, so you came from so far\Naway to study abroad by yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.11,0:05:45.62,Natsu-Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,That's impressive!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.62,0:05:47.82,Natsu-Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Your Japanese is really good, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.82,0:05:49.36,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Thanks...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.63,0:05:50.80,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.80,0:05:54.09,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I understand what's going on now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.09,0:05:55.73,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.73,0:05:58.45,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,But if something happened,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.45,0:06:01.81,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,why not contact your parents back home?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.92,0:06:04.74,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.89,0:06:06.71,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.66,0:06:09.54,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Did something happen to your...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.62,0:06:14.73,Natsu-Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,I think I know how you feel!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.73,0:06:15.82,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Are you an esper?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.82,0:06:16.89,Natsu-Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Takatsuki-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.32,0:06:18.93,Natsu-Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,No, Ichika-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.93,0:06:22.68,Natsu-Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry we brought up such sad memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.68,0:06:24.98,Natsu-Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Kai-kun and I lost our parents, too,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.98,0:06:26.49,Natsu-Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,so I know...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.49,0:06:31.05,Natsu-Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,I really know how you feel!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.05,0:06:32.24,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Wai— Nanami-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.24,0:06:35.49,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,A-Anyway, so that's what's going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.49,0:06:39.82,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,So there shouldn't be a problem with\Nletting her stay here a night, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.82,0:06:41.58,Natsu-Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,A night?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.08,0:06:44.25,Natsu-Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,How about just letting her live here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.90,0:06:45.72,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Nanami-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.11,0:06:49.64,Natsu-Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, I'll be leaving for a pretty \Nlong business trip tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.64,0:06:53.57,Natsu-Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Someone'll need to take care of Kai-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.57,0:06:56.09,Natsu-Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Since she's a senpai from his school, \NI won't have to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.09,0:07:00.18,Natsu-Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,And since she's a girl, she'll be\Nable to cook and do the laundry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.18,0:07:01.30,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'll do my best!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.50,0:07:03.22,Natsu-Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds great.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.77,0:07:05.26,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Nanami-san, you're being too lax!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.26,0:07:07.74,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,You can't let a girl and guy live\Nunder the same roof like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.09,0:07:10.41,Natsu-Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,People have to help each other\Nout when they're on hard times.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.41,0:07:12.57,Natsu-Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,And Kai-kun is nice,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.57,0:07:15.75,Natsu-Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,so he wouldn't try anything funny...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.75,0:07:19.75,Natsu-Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,...just because he's living\Nwith a really cute girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.75,0:07:21.25,Natsu-Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,He wouldn't, would he?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.76,0:07:24.83,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,O-Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.44,0:07:26.52,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,You paused!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.52,0:07:27.66,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,You thought about it for a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.66,0:07:28.96,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,No, I didn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.96,0:07:30.33,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Your eyes are lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.33,0:07:31.18,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,What eyes?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.18,0:07:32.41,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Your eyes right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.41,0:07:34.15,Natsu-Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, so it's settled.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.07,0:07:36.73,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not at all worthy of such favor,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.73,0:07:38.72,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,but I thank you, Onee-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.72,0:07:40.04,Natsu-Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Call me Onee-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.04,0:07:41.85,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, Onee-chan-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.73,0:07:45.61,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,They sound like they're \Ngoing to get married...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.54,0:07:48.78,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to walk Tanigawa home.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.12,0:07:59.66,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,You seem like you're mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.66,0:08:01.01,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.95,0:08:04.70,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,So, Tanigawa...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.95,0:08:06.33,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai, she's...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.42,0:08:08.60,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,You're just helping her out, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.50,0:08:13.27,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,She was in a bad spot and you \Njust helped her out, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.39,0:08:15.08,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.08,0:08:16.28,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,That's all there was to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.28,0:08:17.64,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll trust you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.38,0:08:20.30,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.30,0:08:21.68,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to walk me any farther.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.68,0:08:23.15,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,See you tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.27,0:08:27.11,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.27,0:08:30.56,Natsu-Main,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.87,0:08:34.86,Natsu-Main,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,So that pretty girl is going to \Nstay at Kirishima-kun's house?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.12,0:08:37.23,Natsu-Main,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,How did that happen, Kanna?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.39,0:08:38.92,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.92,0:08:41.63,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,It just kind of kept building up to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.05,0:08:45.70,Natsu-Main,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,But Kirishima-kun lives \Nthere with his sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.93,0:08:48.74,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,His sister is leaving tomorrow \Non a long business trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.14,0:08:50.97,Natsu-Main,Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,What? Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.97,0:08:52.34,Natsu-Main,Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,That happened pretty fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.34,0:08:54.52,Natsu-Main,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do, Tetsuro-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.52,0:08:55.83,Natsu-Main,Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,I've got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.83,0:08:58.02,Natsu-Main,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,Got what?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.02,0:09:00.85,Natsu-Main,Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,I know where we're going \Ntomorrow for our meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.44,0:09:03.49,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.49,0:09:04.59,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.25,0:09:07.06,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Dinner's ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.66,0:09:09.87,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.87,0:09:12.33,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.36,0:09:15.00,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,U-Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.00,0:09:16.24,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Where's my sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.75,0:09:19.12,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,She said she still had to do some packing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.12,0:09:21.01,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,She ate dinner already and is in her room.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.31,0:09:23.24,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.52,0:09:29.39,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Pasta and miso soup?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.39,0:09:30.42,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Pretty normal, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.26,0:09:32.70,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Besides the pairing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.96,0:09:34.61,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Did I get something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.61,0:09:36.02,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.02,0:09:37.46,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have some.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.79,0:09:40.94,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,How is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.15,0:09:43.89,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,A-Are you okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.89,0:09:45.27,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Is it bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.27,0:09:47.97,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's not that...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.29,0:09:51.23,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,It tastes kind of sour...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.66,0:09:54.03,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Is this a cold noodle dish?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.03,0:09:55.04,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.04,0:09:58.28,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,It was hot today, so I thought \Nsomething cold would be good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.57,0:10:02.16,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,I just wasn't expecting the \Nflavor, so I was surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.47,0:10:05.16,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, this cold pasta will be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.81,0:10:10.59,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Could I ask you a question?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.59,0:10:11.53,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.89,0:10:15.37,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you come to study abroad here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.64,0:10:19.08,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Hm...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.30,0:10:24.36,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,There's a place I wanted to visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.06,0:10:26.28,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Where's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.28,0:10:27.91,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Is it around here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.91,0:10:29.79,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,I could take you there, if you'd like.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.79,0:10:32.22,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I don't know where it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.22,0:10:33.48,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.18,0:10:36.88,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,There's a tree there, and a lake.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.66,0:10:40.61,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't really have anything \Nspecial to identify it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.61,0:10:42.56,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,That'd make it hard to find.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.25,0:10:44.46,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.10,0:10:47.32,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,But I'd still like to go there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.20,0:10:52.75,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,That was one hectic day.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.17,0:10:57.81,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,And I have to have a meeting \Nwith everyone tomorrow...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.72,0:11:05.00,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,How am I going to explain this to them?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.69,0:11:06.68,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.91,0:11:08.94,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.21,0:11:12.28,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,It's spreading?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.80,0:11:13.99,Natsu-Italic,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah, not too long ago, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.55,0:11:18.12,Natsu-Italic,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Did you think he'd get better \Nif you embraced him?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.54,0:11:21.63,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Embraced...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.63,0:11:24.87,Natsu-Italic,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.87,0:11:27.12,Natsu-Italic,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,I need to give you medical \Nattention right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.12,0:11:30.20,Natsu-Italic,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Pain, pain, go away.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.20,0:11:30.69,Natsu-Italic,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Kiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.48,0:11:33.05,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.05,0:11:34.24,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,That'd never happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.05,0:11:40.38,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't working.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.56,0:11:42.22,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't look like I can repair it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.61,0:11:44.86,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Rinon, how is the quan linkage looking?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.83,0:11:49.35,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,It's bugging out pretty badly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.09,0:11:53.77,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't regret what's happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.97,0:11:56.81,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,I was able to make it to this planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.73,0:12:01.70,Natsu-Italic,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I was too tired \Nfrom everything going on,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.51,0:12:06.49,Natsu-Italic,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,but as soon as I hit my bed, \NI fell right asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.00,0:12:11.68,Natsu-Italic,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't even have any dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.12,0:12:12.63,Natsu-Ep-Title2,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 2\N\NTogether with Senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.18,0:12:15.27,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Kaito-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.58,0:12:16.67,Natsu-Main,Icihka,0000,0000,0000,,Kaito-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.67,0:12:18.30,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Wake up, Kaito-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.30,0:12:20.55,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan-san said she's \Ngoing to leave soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.79,0:12:26.29,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know it was so late...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.16,0:12:29.82,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.82,0:12:30.96,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,You're wearing...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.96,0:12:33.60,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I borrowed it from Onee-chan-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.12,0:12:38.36,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Sleepwear from this area \Nis a little embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.36,0:12:40.57,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,I-It really is!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.57,0:12:41.98,Natsu-Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Kai-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.98,0:12:44.58,Natsu-Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Your sister is leaving!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.58,0:12:48.36,Natsu-Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't say goodbye, I'm going to cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.36,0:12:49.91,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be right down!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.18,0:12:59.23,Natsu-Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Kaito-kun, make sure you don't get sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.23,0:13:01.74,Natsu-Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Try not to use too much \Nout of your living expenses.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.74,0:13:04.14,Natsu-Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure you study, \Nget along with your friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.14,0:13:05.27,Natsu-Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,and don't stay up too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.27,0:13:07.68,Natsu-Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,I'm getting sad, so goodbye and take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.21,0:13:11.71,Natsu-Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Ichika-chan, take care of Kai-kun for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.05,0:13:15.26,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,It's time to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.51,0:13:21.05,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,She finally left.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.52,0:13:22.49,Natsu-Main,Icihka,0000,0000,0000,,Kaito-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.55,0:13:24.51,Natsu-Main,Icihka,0000,0000,0000,,You lonely?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.04,0:13:28.35,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,A little, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.58,0:13:31.05,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah, Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.24,0:13:34.83,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,There's a place I want to \Nstop by before we head back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.01,0:13:36.55,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,A place you want to stop by?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.55,0:13:38.39,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Nee-san asked me to.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.39,0:13:39.67,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan-san did?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.67,0:13:42.93,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you need to get\Nsome everyday clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.83,0:13:48.91,Natsu-Italic,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,She's...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.54,0:13:51.91,Natsu-Italic,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,...a little strange sometimes,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.35,0:13:53.08,Natsu-Italic,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.45,0:13:58.03,Natsu-Italic,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,She's cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.67,0:14:06.37,Total,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Total due
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.60,0:14:10.18,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,This should be enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.18,0:14:11.21,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.21,0:14:12.66,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,That was a lot of fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.11,0:14:16.17,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Shopping really is a girl's greatest pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.75,0:14:20.42,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,I have to tell Onee-chan-san\Nthank you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.42,0:14:23.19,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,You can wait until she calls us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.19,0:14:24.41,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.65,0:14:28.35,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? It's open.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.92,0:14:30.10,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.10,0:14:30.55,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.83,0:14:32.62,Natsu-Main,Remon,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're late.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.28,0:14:34.85,Natsu-Main,Remon,0000,0000,0000,,I almost couldn't wait any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.85,0:14:35.65,Natsu-Main,Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,Yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.65,0:14:36.95,Natsu-Main,Mio/Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.95,0:14:38.44,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.75,0:14:40.43,Natsu-Main,Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,We said yesterday we were going...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.43,0:14:42.09,Natsu-Main,Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,...to have a kick-off meeting \Nfor the movie, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.68,0:14:46.28,Natsu-Main,Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but we all decided on your \Nhouse as the place to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.28,0:14:47.75,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,That's not the problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.75,0:14:48.87,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.12,0:14:51.30,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Close enough to go shopping \Ntogether already, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.30,0:14:53.52,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's not it...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.52,0:14:55.95,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,How did you get in the house, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.95,0:14:59.34,Natsu-Main,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,You should use a better lock.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.83,0:15:01.25,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Don't just unlock it without asking.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.50,0:15:03.30,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,That's really illegal!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.30,0:15:06.72,Natsu-Main,Remon,0000,0000,0000,,But I have to do my due diligence.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.95,0:15:08.95,Natsu-Main,Remon,0000,0000,0000,,On where my good friend is staying.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.05,0:15:10.98,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,How did you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.07,0:15:13.46,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Tanigawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.89,0:15:18.40,Natsu-Main,Remon,0000,0000,0000,,Now that we're all here,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.66,0:15:21.23,Natsu-Main,Remon,0000,0000,0000,,we can begin our first \Nmeeting regarding Director...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.23,0:15:25.73,Natsu-Main,Remon,0000,0000,0000,,...Kaito Kirishima's work that we \Nvolunteers will put together.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.73,0:15:27.59,Natsu-Main,Remon,0000,0000,0000,,It will begin now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.96,0:15:29.31,Natsu-Main,Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Director.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.62,0:15:32.13,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have to call me that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.13,0:15:34.46,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, why is she in charge?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.46,0:15:36.67,Natsu-Main,Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,Why not? She's an upperclassman, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.68,0:15:41.99,Natsu-Main,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,So what type of movie are we making?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.30,0:15:45.32,Natsu-Main,Remon,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be using this script \NI wrote for the film.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.72,0:15:47.73,Natsu-Main,Remon,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, the idea was \Ndeveloped over twenty years.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.73,0:15:48.78,Natsu-Main,Remon,0000,0000,0000,,The writing took five.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.78,0:15:49.50,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.50,0:15:51.10,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,What's the story like?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.68,0:15:56.28,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,In the 23rd century, mobile weapons \Nare used across the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.28,0:16:00.05,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be a huge flick that's far beyond what Hollywood could pull off.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.05,0:16:00.84,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,That's not happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.84,0:16:03.49,Natsu-Main,Remon,0000,0000,0000,,We'll do it all in CG, so it'll be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.49,0:16:05.82,Natsu-Main,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,We might not need a camera, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.82,0:16:08.80,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Shouldn't we do something\Nwe know we can do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.80,0:16:10.82,Natsu-Main,Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,How about a story related to school?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.01,0:16:13.96,Natsu-Main,Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure the school will \Nlet us film there, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.96,0:16:15.91,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's one way to play it safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.91,0:16:17.49,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,What would we do for the story?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.87,0:16:19.86,Natsu-Main,Remon,0000,0000,0000,,How about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.86,0:16:22.08,Natsu-Main,Remon,0000,0000,0000,,Zombies appear at the\Nschool out of nowhere,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.08,0:16:23.57,Natsu-Main,Remon,0000,0000,0000,,and the main characters,\Nthe only people left alive—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.57,0:16:24.50,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,That's not happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.96,0:16:27.97,Natsu-Main,Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have any requests, Ichika-senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.41,0:16:29.96,Natsu-Main,Remon,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Kirishima-kun, you're quite the brave one.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.28,0:16:29.52,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.52,0:16:31.68,Natsu-Main,Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,You're the lead, so you should \Ntell us what you'd like to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.96,0:16:31.49,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Huh? Wa-Wai—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.61,0:16:35.62,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Hm... It doesn't have anything \Nto do with the story,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.99,0:16:38.48,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,but I'd like to see some pretty scenery.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.04,0:16:41.33,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,I just got here, so I'd like to go...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.33,0:16:44.82,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,...all over the place and\Nsee different things.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.67,0:16:48.56,Natsu-Italic,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,There's a place I wanted to visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.29,0:16:52.96,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, s-sorry for being so abstract.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.58,0:16:55.07,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,It sounds good to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.07,0:16:56.47,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go around to different places.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.47,0:16:58.03,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost summer break anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.03,0:16:59.23,Natsu-Main,Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds good.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.57,0:17:02.97,Natsu-Main,Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,We can film the movie and \Nhave fun at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.97,0:17:05.97,Natsu-Main,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,I think we'd end up just messing around.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.97,0:17:07.27,Natsu-Main,Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,That wouldn't be so bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.95,0:17:11.19,Natsu-Main,Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like we have to put \Ntogether a movie no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.74,0:17:13.64,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go all over the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.64,0:17:14.21,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.71,0:17:17.33,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,You might find that place you want to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.33,0:17:19.28,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Kaito-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.79,0:17:23.34,Natsu-Main,Remon,0000,0000,0000,,We'll think about the content of the movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.34,0:17:27.84,Natsu-Main,Remon,0000,0000,0000,,But let's all toast for \Nthe success of the film.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.84,0:17:29.46,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.93,0:17:32.66,Natsu-Main,Remon,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, cheers.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.66,0:17:34.37,Natsu-Main,Everyone,0000,0000,0000,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.91,0:17:37.74,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,What is this, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.74,0:17:39.11,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,It tastes pretty strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.11,0:17:41.82,Natsu-Main,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,But it has a bit of \Nsweetness that's kind of good.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.82,0:17:43.01,Natsu-Main,Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have any more?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.01,0:17:47.10,Natsu-Main,Remon,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I brought a lot with me, \Nso have as much as you'd like.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.27,0:17:59.15,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Revolution! And I'm out this round!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.57,0:18:09.58,Natsu-Italic,Remon,0000,0000,0000,,Smirk.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.93,0:18:24.58,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Remon-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.12,0:18:28.31,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,What's this drink called?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.61,0:18:30.32,Natsu-Main,Remon,0000,0000,0000,,Dynamite Drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.50,0:18:32.21,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.21,0:18:33.76,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,That works!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.31,0:18:37.52,Natsu-Main,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,Dynamite!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.21,0:18:40.76,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.76,0:18:43.17,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,I kinda feel hot...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.49,0:18:44.27,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Hot?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.70,0:18:47.95,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, my body feels warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.65,0:18:50.37,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Your body...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.65,0:18:51.45,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.99,0:18:53.68,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,I-I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.18,0:18:57.33,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That sounds like a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.52,0:19:00.67,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.67,0:19:02.69,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,What are you guys doing \Nout there by yourselves?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.87,0:19:04.82,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Come here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.58,0:19:08.40,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Tanigawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.40,0:19:11.37,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,You think I'm disturbing you two, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.86,0:19:12.83,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.15,0:19:15.12,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.12,0:19:17.04,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,What about you, Senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.04,0:19:18.67,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't thinking that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.67,0:19:20.98,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to be staying here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.85,0:19:23.08,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.08,0:19:25.29,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are going to live together.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.29,0:19:26.71,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.31,0:19:30.35,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost summer break.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.72,0:19:32.68,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,You two will be alone together all day...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.10,0:19:34.11,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.11,0:19:34.91,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.91,0:19:35.79,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Ichika-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.79,0:19:36.78,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.78,0:19:39.41,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get straight to the point!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.41,0:19:43.86,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,How do you feel about Kaito-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.71,0:19:47.93,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,I-I...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.93,0:19:51.74,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Kaito-kun helped me when \NI was in a time of need...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.96,0:19:54.05,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Not that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.05,0:19:57.09,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,I'm asking what you think of him!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.09,0:19:58.25,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.71,0:20:01.06,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.05,0:20:10.85,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.09,0:20:15.56,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.18,0:20:17.12,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,A biological entity...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.12,0:20:18.48,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.48,0:20:20.81,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,It's my p-pet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.81,0:20:22.03,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Its name is Rinon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.03,0:20:23.77,Natsu-Main,Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,Is there even an animal like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.77,0:20:24.88,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,It's really weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.88,0:20:26.20,Natsu-Main,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,But it's kinda cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.20,0:20:27.86,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,It's dancing, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.03,0:20:31.58,Natsu-Main,Remon,0000,0000,0000,,Now that things are really getting started,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.93,0:20:35.31,Natsu-Main,Remon,0000,0000,0000,,we'll play my special version \Nof the "King" game.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.31,0:20:37.38,Natsu-Main,Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}That sounds good!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.88,0:20:37.38,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,King game?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.38,0:20:39.32,Natsu-Main,Remon,0000,0000,0000,,You'll understand when we play.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.02,0:20:42.29,Natsu-Main,Everyone,0000,0000,0000,,Who's the king?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.29,0:20:47.76,King,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,King
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.52,0:20:43.73,Natsu-Main,Remon,0000,0000,0000,,It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.31,0:20:45.81,Natsu-Main,Remon,0000,0000,0000,,Now, to start off easy,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.81,0:20:48.96,Natsu-Main,Remon,0000,0000,0000,,number three, flick number one in\Nthe forehead, as hard as you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.96,0:20:49.83,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.83,0:20:52.10,Natsu-Main,Remon,0000,0000,0000,,Number four, hit number one.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.10,0:20:53.20,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid Kai-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.59,0:20:54.71,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Why is this all happening to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.71,0:20:56.70,Natsu-Main,Remon,0000,0000,0000,,Number five, kiss number four.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.22,0:20:56.70,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}What the hell is with this drawing?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.70,0:20:57.50,Natsu-Main,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,Kiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.27,0:21:00.50,Natsu-Main,Remon,0000,0000,0000,,Number three, take off your pants.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.50,0:21:01.67,Natsu-Main,Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.67,0:21:03.42,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you taking off your boxers, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.42,0:21:04.41,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Pervert!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.61,0:21:06.70,Natsu-Main,Remon,0000,0000,0000,,Number four, make a pose\Nlike a female panther.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.90,0:21:10.01,Natsu-Main,Remon,0000,0000,0000,,And number two...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.01,0:21:10.95,Natsu-Main,Remon,0000,0000,0000,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.50,0:21:12.75,Natsu-Main,Remon,0000,0000,0000,,You and number one...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.79,0:21:14.95,Natsu-Main,Remon,0000,0000,0000,,...must have sex.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.26,0:21:17.03,Natsu-Main,Everyone,0000,0000,0000,,Not happening!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.71,0:21:28.38,Natsu-Main,Remon,0000,0000,0000,,That was wonderful, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.38,0:21:30.77,Natsu-Main,Remon,0000,0000,0000,,This movie is shaping up very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.12,0:21:37.21,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Kaito-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.55,0:21:38.59,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.59,0:21:41.59,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.57,0:21:43.75,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,How about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.57,0:21:46.28,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.28,0:21:47.15,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.60,0:21:50.96,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what that drink was.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.56,0:21:53.90,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,My head hurts all of a sudden...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.90,0:21:55.35,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Kaito-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.65,0:21:59.27,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry, Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.20,0:22:05.71,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Close your eyes for a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.32,0:22:10.16,Natsu-Italic,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Rinon!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.72,0:22:18.70,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,How is it now?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.49,0:22:20.46,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.46,0:22:21.42,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.59,0:22:23.96,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.67,0:22:28.26,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.12,0:22:32.73,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid Kai-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.54,0:22:36.17,Natsu-Main,Tetsuro,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the stupid one.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.67,0:22:39.71,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.72,0:22:43.37,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.69,0:22:44.78,Natsu-Main,Kaito,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.57,0:22:47.48,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,You can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.55,0:22:50.92,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,You can't say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.52,0:22:53.62,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.85,0:22:56.19,Natsu-Main,Ichika,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.41,0:23:40.35,Natsu-Next-Ep-Title2,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 3\N\NSenpai says...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.28,0:23:34.42,Natsu-Main,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,Kanna, Kirishima-kun's out today.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.42,0:23:36.36,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad! We have to go visit him!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.36,0:23:37.73,Natsu-Main,Kanna,0000,0000,0000,,It's our top priority!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.73,0:23:40.37,Natsu-Main,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,That was the one thing you \Nshouldn't have said.
